com.mapbox.api.directions.v5.models

Class BannerComponents

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.api.directions.v5.models.BannerComponents
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public abstract class BannerComponents
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A part of the BannerText which includes a snippet of the full banner text instruction. In cases where data is avaliable, an image url will be provided to visually include a road shield. To receive this information, your request must have MapboxDirections.bannerInstructions() set to true.
    Since:
    3.0.0
    See Also:
